### ----------------------------------------
### 1. Get Profile - Success (Any Authenticated User)
### ----------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: 200
### { success: true, message: "Profile retrieved successfully", data: { user: {...} } }


### ----------------------------------------
### 2. Get Profile - Unauthorized (No Token)
### ----------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/profile

### Expected: 401
### { success: false, message: "No token provided" or "Unauthorized" }


### ----------------------------------------
### 3. Get All Users - Success (Admin Only)
### ----------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: 200 (if admin token)
### { success: true, message: "Users retrieved successfully", data: { users: [...] } }

### Expected: 403 (if non-admin token)
### { success: false, message: "Forbidden" or "Access denied" }


### ----------------------------------------
### 4. Get User by ID - Success (Admin Only)
### ----------------------------------------
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/<valid_user_id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: 200
### { success: true, message: "User retrieved successfully", data: { user: {...} } }


### ----------------------------------------
### 5. Update User - Success (Admin Only)
### ----------------------------------------
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/<valid_user_id>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "username": "updatedUsername",
  "role": "problem_setter"
}

### Expected: 200
### { success: true, message: "User updated successfully", data: { user: {...} } }


### ----------------------------------------
### 6. Delete User - Success (Admin Only)
### ----------------------------------------
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/users/<valid_user_id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: 200
### { success: true, message: "User deleted successfully" }
